{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-462-permutation-of-3-smooth-numbers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Problem 462: Transformacija broja 3-smooth","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>3-smooth broj je celi broj koji nema premični faktor veći od 3. Za celi broj $N$, definišemo $S(N)$ kao skup 3-smooth brojeva manjih ili jednakih $N$. Na primer, $S(20) = \\{1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 8, 9, 12, 16, 18\\}$.</p>\n<p>Definisemo $F(N)$ kao broj promena $S(N)$, gde svaki element dolazi nakon svih svojih premih delitelja.</p>\n<p>Ovo je jedan od mogućih promena za $N = 20$.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1, 2, 4, 3, 9, 8, 16, 6, 18, 12.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ovo nije važeća transformacija zato što 12 dolazi pre svog delitelja 6.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1, 2, 4, 3, 9, 8, 12, 16, 6, 18.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Možemo potvrditi da $F(6) = 5$, $F(8) = 9$, $F(20) = 450$ i $F(1000) ≈ 8.8521816557e\\,21$.</p>\n<p>Pronađite $F({10}^{18})$. Odgovor napišite u naučnoj notaciji, zaokružen na deset cifara posle decimalne tačke. Koristite malo slovo <code>e</code> za razdvajanje mantise i eksponenta. Na primer, ako je odgovor $112\\,233\\,445\\,566\\,778\\,899$, format odgovora bi bio <code>1.1223344557e17</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f53b1000cf542c51004d","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302137,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-462-permutation-of-3-smooth-numbers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function permutationOf3SmoothNumbers() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npermutationOf3SmoothNumbers();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>permutationOf3SmoothNumbers()</code> Trebalo bi da vrati niz karaktera.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(typeof permutationOf3SmoothNumbers(), 'string');"},{"text":"<p><code>permutationOf3SmoothNumbers()</code> treba da vrati sekvencu karaktera <code>5.5350769703e1512</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(permutationOf3SmoothNumbers(), '5.5350769703e1512');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-462-permutation-of-3-smooth-numbers","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-463-a-weird-recurrence-relation","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-461-almost-pi","id":"5900f53b1000cf542c51004d","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-462-permutation-of-3-smooth-numbers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}